description.en:
Wrapped Kadena (wKDA) is a 1:1 equivalent of Kadena (KDA) represented as an ERC-20 on Ethereum.

About wrapped.com:

Wrapped.com lets investors use their digital assets to lend, borrow, and trade on all major DeFi platforms. Each wrapped asset is fully-collateralized and held with a qualified custodian.

Wrapped.com is a collaboration of Tokensoft Inc. with leading custodians and other financial institutions. Tokensoft provides the technology layer via Wrapped.com that allows users to wrap their KDA into wKDA.
